## 3. Scope Rationale

KodeVibe is a TypeScript-heavy v0.1.0 code-vibe tooling project under registry-affirmed ownership. The ABSORPTION_DELTA intent is "AFFIRM with proposed sub-absorption of CODE/inference helpers into pheno-runtime npm-pkg sub-crate". The full-codebase square root is preserved — we intend to lift a 2.0.0 minor release to absorb the CODE/inference helpers as a separate npm-pkg under `pheno-runtime` rather than fold the whole repo into a sister crate. This preserves front-end + UX intact.

